output:
I'm in the cut with the heavy drum beats,
Bringing the heat and flow that's so complete,
Making the beat stop and make 'em retreat,
It's the truth, no need for deceit.

You can try to hate but it ain't no use,
Ain't no way that you can cop my blues,
Cause I'm ill with these rhymes and I'm always in the mood,
To bring 'em to life like an electric juiced.

Word around town, better spread the news,
Top of the line, don't want no slop in my shoes,
Keep it pushin' forward, ain't comin' loose,
Got the skills that nobody can refuse.
